    <h2>🔴 Priority 1: A.3 Credentials Audit - Execution Phase 1 (3-4 hours)</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Execute audit per scope plan from Jan 5:</strong> Scan codebase for hardcoded credentials, classify findings, identify quick wins.</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Scan Codebase for Hardcoded Credentials:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Search: grep/rg for patterns (password=, secret=, key=, token=, apikey)</li>
                <li>Check: .env files in version control and git history</li>
                <li>Review: db_config.json for exposed database credentials</li>
                <li>Audit: API configuration files (Proxmox, Cloudflare, Ollama)</li>
                <li>Document: All findings with file path, line number, risk level</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Classify Findings:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Separate: Hardcoded vs env vars vs secrets manager vs insecure</li>
                <li>Rate: Risk level (🔴 CRITICAL, 🟠 HIGH, 🟡 MEDIUM, 🟢 LOW)</li>
                <li>Identify: Quick wins (can move immediately)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Create Interim Report:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>File: /Documentation/A3_Audit_Execution_Phase1_Report.tt</li>
                <li>Include: Findings summary, quick wins identified</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> Credentials findings list + interim audit report</p>

    <h2>🟠 Priority 2: B.1 Docker Secrets - Phase 2 (2-3 hours)</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Support A.3 remediation:</strong> Implement Docker Secrets infrastructure for credentials identified in A.3 Phase 1 audit.</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Complete Docker Secrets integration:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Create: docker-compose override with secrets for A.3 findings</li>
                <li>Reference: secrets in service containers</li>
                <li>Test: Multi-stage deployment (dev, staging, prod)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Assess documentation gaps:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Identify: Missing documentation for controllers (from earlier audit)</li>
                <li>Flag: Broken links and outdated references</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Create C.1 Audit Plan:</strong>
